            "default":"<p>Users who pay a $1 deposit during the warm-up can enjoy $10 off on hat heat press (machine or bundle)；</p><p>Each user can enjoy the deal once, and no refunds are available.</p><p>Validity: 20th Feb, 2024 - 5th Mar, 20</p><p>Code: S20</p>"
        },
        {
            "type":"text",
            "id":"coupon",
            "label":"Coupon",
